{
  "stem": "15943.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the inspector came, wanted to see, you know, how well those children are doing at that school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she called-- you want to show off with your good students, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So one of the teachers-- it was Polish class, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yoskowitz. ?] And she says to me-- it's funny.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My Yiddish name is Riva, or Rivkala, basically.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Polish version was [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Reginka, ?] like you would put English.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so, [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Reginka, ?] can you tell me what's on the picture.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a picture on the wall.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I couldn't see the picture, but I wouldn't say that I can't see the picture.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I just made up a story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was telling her what the boat-- where the boat is going.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And everybody started laughing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I-- what are they laughing?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I didn't know what they were laughing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And him, he laughed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The teacher laughed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then when they left the classroom, I climbed on the desk, looked up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a bowl of fruit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I made out a most interesting story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So these are the experiences that, you know, kind of stuck in, in my mind.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The school wasn't closed up, so I guess we passed the test.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Till the war-- till the beginning of the war, 1939.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the ghetto, we still had for a while-- we had some classes, only for a few months.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then all the teachers were taken away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Most of them were taken away before that or they escaped to Russia or whatever they went because the educators were the first ones to be taken away-- educators, clergy of all faiths, political leaders.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were left without teachers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the beginning, we still had a little bit in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
